347
00:24:36,730 --> 00:24:39,320
Never mind, I'll clean up. Get some rest.

348
00:24:39,320 --> 00:24:40,779
Oh, thanks.

349
00:24:40,779 --> 00:24:43,200
Do you actually have a boyfriend?

350
