529
00:37:16,710 --> 00:37:18,560
What are you talking about?

530
00:37:19,340 --> 00:37:21,399
By the way, Seon Woo, I had no idea you'd come.

531
00:37:21,399 --> 00:37:23,539
You've never participated in things like this before.

